---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Projects from "../components/Projects.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
const pageTitle = "Home Page";
---

<style>
  h2 {
    color: var(--color-brand-50);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }
  h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-brand-50);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <div class="flex flex-col absolute left-2 top-20 text-brand-500 leading-8">
    <a href="#work">#&nbsp;repos</a>
    <a href="#about">#&nbsp;about</a>
  </div>
  <Hero />
  <Projects />
  <!-- === About === -->
  <section id="about" class="about section-pad">
    <h2 class="text-2xl text-center">about&nbsp;me</h2>
    <h3>Hello, I'm Marcus! ðŸ‘‹</h3>
    <p>
      Welcome to my world where technology meets passion and curiosity fuels
      innovation. My journey into the tech realm is a testament to the power of
      self-learning and determination. With just a high school diploma in hand,
      I embarked on a path that led me to become a seasoned Systems Architect,
      and here's how my adventure unfolded.
    </p>
    <h3>The Unconventional Start</h3>
    <p>
      Diving into the tech industry with no formal background, my career began
      at Endurance International Group, a conglomerate of renowned web hosting
      companies. As a Tier 1 Tech Support agent, I was the first line of contact
      for customers, and it was here, amidst daily challenges, that my
      fascination with technology blossomed. Despite my initial unfamiliarity
      with the domain, including the intricacies of DNS, my eagerness to learn
      quickly set me apart.
    </p>
    <h3>The Self-Taught Journey</h3>
    <p>
      My thirst for knowledge led me to Lynda.com (now LinkedIn Learning), where
      I delved into the realms of web development. Starting with HTML, CSS, and
      Javascript, I ventured into learning various programming languages such as
      Bash, Perl, Python, and Javascript. This exploration wasn't just
      theoretical; it translated into practical solutions at work. I mastered
      the art of automation, often through unconventional means like web
      scraping and session keys, out of necessity due to my limited access as a
      Tier 1 tech.
    </p>
    <h3>The Rapid Ascent</h3>
    <p>
      My unique approach to problem-solving didn't go unnoticed. Within months,
      I was promoted to Web Concierge, then to the WP Live team, where I
      co-founded a service focused on WordPress development. My journey didn't
      stop there. I advanced to the Professional Services department, enjoying
      roles that involved custom coding and complex project management.
      Eventually, I ascended to a Linux Admin role, fine-tuning my skills in
      server management and networking.
    </p>
    <h3>Expanding Horizons</h3>
    <p>
      Seeking new challenges, I joined Caris Life Sciences as a Linux Engineer,
      further honing my expertise in biotechnology contexts. My current role as
      a Systems Architect at BankSITE Services epitomizes my growth. Here, I
      single-handedly manage the infrastructure, encompassing two data centers,
      monitoring, security, and virtualization. My mantra is automation, the
      cornerstone of efficiency in my work.
    </p>
    <h3>Looking Ahead</h3>
    <p>
      As someone who never stops learning, I'm now exploring the fascinating
      worlds of Machine Learning, AI, and Algorithmic Trading. These fields
      represent the cutting edge of technology, aligning perfectly with my
      passion for coding and data. Thank you for joining me on this incredible
      journey. I am a living example that with passion and perseverance, the
      sky's the limit in the tech world!
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
